    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/1f56d4a25366466f1995753ab8800d62.avif?t=1755529376\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><br>在过山车修理工那里，您可以修复被破坏的或是有破损的游乐场。在那个由利奥（Leo）和诺亚（Noah）的两个兄弟创立的小公司中，每个人都拥有不同的技能，并且能承受巨大的挑战：修复破损的过山车或其他景点。他们通过诊断损坏、维修、清洁和测试。最后，您能享受所有被修复的景点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/71d28f809b5853ed0fb0c4d51402da87.poster.avif?t=1755529376\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/71d28f809b5853ed0fb0c4d51402da87.webm?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>其中，高空工作是最大的挑战。但是在这里，兄弟之间的合作是成功的基础。通常，您不得不爬到高处，只是为了拧一个可能在排队时造成悲剧的小螺钉。当您想进入云层作业时，请务必记得带上齐全的工具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/3f625bc1401739fb821be7cb6798aaec.poster.avif?t=1755529376\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/3f625bc1401739fb821be7cb6798aaec.webm?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/3f625bc1401739fb821be7cb6798aaec.mp4?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>幸运的是，有一个诊断控制台能供您使用，如果没有它的帮助，您就基本不可能会准确地发现故障。这是您的命令中心，您将通过它找出问题所在，但您必须保持细心和认真，因为并非所有地故障都显而易见。当然，最重要的任务是修理和更换损坏的零件。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/c52d9d8f281ba8965fd4df0433d334fc.poster.avif?t=1755529376\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/c52d9d8f281ba8965fd4df0433d334fc.webm?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/c52d9d8f281ba8965fd4df0433d334fc.mp4?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>该镇被废弃了很长时间，因此，您不仅需要修复损坏之处，还需要做很多清理工作，从而能给它带来新的光彩，您还需要为很多零件做润滑和激活地工作。这并非是一件易事，您必须提防流浪汉、大批的老鼠或其他新居民。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/f4408594027785fd765295503761d9ea.poster.avif?t=1755529376\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/f4408594027785fd765295503761d9ea.webm?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/f4408594027785fd765295503761d9ea.mp4?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一个只有兄弟俩的小型家族企业，对他们来说是一个很大的挑战。兄弟之间的情况有所不同，但利奥和诺亚能够充分地相互理解，并在技能上产生互补地效果。根据您的需要，他们二人会结合两者的经验，进行充分配合来完成任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/22f5028b671bfff58e9e48c09dc7bc61.poster.avif?t=1755529376\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/22f5028b671bfff58e9e48c09dc7bc61.webm?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/22f5028b671bfff58e9e48c09dc7bc61.mp4?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>过山车修理工这一职业并不是一份简单的工作，您需要不断地学习和提升，学会使用新工具，同时对它们进行开发和改进。购买新工具会使您的工作更有效率；应用新的机械能让您更快更好地工作，同时也会给您带来很多乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/af52d6b86946f0dd609ddbb0169042d6.poster.avif?t=1755529376\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/af52d6b86946f0dd609ddbb0169042d6.webm?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280660/extras/af52d6b86946f0dd609ddbb0169042d6.mp4?t=1755529376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>最后，这是您工作中最重要的部分：在移交给客人之前，应对每个景点进行测试。请务必记住，这个部分非常重要。您必须保证它是被完美地修复成功了，因为如果你犯了一个错误……我简直不敢想后果会有多严重了。您一定会成功的，希望您能享受其中的乐趣！",
